&lt;p>The world around us is either a warfield or playground. &lt;br>
If it is warfield then we keep fighting. &lt;br>
If it is a playground, then we keep playing. &lt;br>
If we are interested in doing karma then &lt;br>
these are two kinds of Karma options before us. &lt;br>
In one karma one gets exhausted and wants to quit, &lt;br>
in another one enjoys and wants to continue the game.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>